snippet.title: Rogue Sentry | Release Trailer
snippet.description: Rogue Sentry is out now on itch.io! 😳✨ A twin-stick adventure shoot-em-up about a sentry droid who turns rogue to save humanity. You can get it now at https://mdev.itch.io/rogue-sentry Enjoy!
